274	## Part 4: Navigation Architecture
275	
276	### Navigator Structure (GoRouter)
277	```
278	ShellRoute (BottomNavigationBar)
279	├── Home (/')
280	├── Browse (/browse)         ← contains Cycle Tracking, Weight & Nutrition
281	├── Library (/library)       ← contains Education, Health Log
282	└── Profile (/profile)      ← contains Settings, Mindfulness
283	```
284	
285	### Bottom Navigation (4 tabs)
286	| Tab | Label | Icon | Route |
287	|---|---|---|---|
288	| Home | Home | `Icons.home_outlined` | `/` |
289	| Browse | Browse | `Icons.search_outlined` | `/browse` |
290	| Library | Library | `Icons.bookmark_outline` | `/library` |
291	| Profile | Profile | `Icons.person_outline` | `/profile` |
292	
293	### Push Routes (detail screens)
294	| Screen | Route | Parent |
295	|---|---|---|
296	| Cycle Tracking | `/cycle-tracking` | Browse tab |
297	| Weight & Nutrition | `/weight-nutrition` | Browse tab |
298	| Pregnancy Progress | `/pregnancy-progress` | Home tab |
299	| Mindfulness | `/mindfulness` | Profile tab |
300	| Health Log | `/health-log` | Library tab |
301	| Mood & Wellness | `/mood-wellness` | Library tab |
302	| Education | `/education` | Library tab |
303	| Article Reader | `/article-reader/:id` | Education |
304	| Settings | `/settings` | Profile tab |
305	
306	### Modal Overlays
307	| Overlay | Route | Type | Parent Screen |
308	|---|---|---|---|
309	| Breathing Exercise | `overlay:breathing-exercise` | full-sheet overlay | Mindfulness |
310	| Stretching Guide | `overlay:stretching-guide` | bottom-sheet | Mindfulness |
311	| Mode Selector | `overlay:mode-selector` | bottom-sheet | Home |
312	| Symptom Detail | `overlay:symptom-detail` | bottom-sheet | Health Log |
313	
314	### Deep Links
315	- `babybump://home` → `/`
316	- `babybump://browse` → `/browse`
317	- `babybump://education/:id` → `/article-reader/:id`
318	- `babybump://settings` → `/settings`
319	
320	---
321	
322	## Part 5: Data Context
323	
324	### Entities
325	
326	| Entity | Key Fields | Provider | Screens |
327	|---|---|---|---|
328	| `PregnancyProfile` | dueDate, lastPeriodDate, currentWeek | `PregnancyProfileProvider` | Home, Pregnancy Progress, Settings |
329	| `CycleEntry` | startDate, endDate, notes, isIrregular | `CycleEntryProvider` | Cycle Tracking |
330	| `WeightEntry` | date, weightKg, note | `WeightEntryProvider` | Weight & Nutrition |
331	| `MoodEntry` | date, moodScore (1-5), note, energyLevel | `MoodEntryProvider` | Home, Mood & Wellness |
332	| `SymptomEntry` | date, symptomType, severity (1-3), notes | `SymptomEntryProvider` | Health Log |
333	| `DoctorVisit` | date, doctorName, notes, nextVisitDate | `DoctorVisitProvider` | Health Log |
334	| `Reminder` | title, date, category, isEnabled | `ReminderProvider` | Health Log |
335	| `SelfCareCheckState` | date, checkedItems: List<String> | `SelfCareCheckStateProvider` | Home, Mindfulness |
336	| `Article` | id, title, topic, content, imageUrl, isBookmarked | `ArticleProvider` | Education, Article Reader |
337	| `UserPreferences` | name, notificationsEnabled, dueDate | `UserPreferencesProvider` | Settings |
338	
339	### Relationships
340	- `PregnancyProfile.currentWeek` drives all week-based content (tips, body changes, nutrition advice)
341	- `MoodEntryProvider` aggregates mood data for `MoodWellnessScreen` trend charts
342	- `SelfCareCheckState` stores today's checklist state, consumed by Home dashboard
343	- `ArticleProvider` tracks bookmarks, consumed by Library tab
344	
